									<time class="pr-[20px] hidden lg:inline-block">2024.4.17</time>
									<span class="tracking-widest">『wowaka 歌詞集』寄稿</span>
								</a>
							</li>
							<li class="mb-[20px] overflow-hidden whitespace-nowrap text-ellipsis">
								<a href="https://pinocchiop.com/news/992" class = "hover:text-black hover:bg-white  w-full py-[4px] px-[15px] lg:py-[8px] lg:px-[23px] text-white text-[20px] bg-transparent block rounded-lg overflow-hidden text-ellipsis border-white border-solid border-2">
									<time class="pr-[20px] hidden lg:inline-block">2024.2.22</time>
									<span class="tracking-widest">猫又おかゆ 新曲「ネコカブリーナ」楽曲提供</span>
								</a>
							</li>
							<li class="mb-[20px] overflow-hidden whitespace-nowrap text-ellipsis">
