									<time class="pr-[20px] hidden lg:inline-block">2024.2.5</time>
									<span class="tracking-widest">「全国バンド図鑑 2024上半期 vol.18」掲載</span>
								</a>
							</li>
							<li class="mb-[20px] overflow-hidden whitespace-nowrap text-ellipsis">
								<a href="https://pinocchiop.com/news/986" class = "hover:text-black hover:bg-white  w-full py-[4px] px-[15px] lg:py-[8px] lg:px-[23px] text-white text-[20px] bg-transparent block rounded-lg overflow-hidden text-ellipsis border-white border-solid border-2">
									<time class="pr-[20px] hidden lg:inline-block">2024.1.27</time>
									<span class="tracking-widest">「ピノキオピー 15th アニバーサリーフェア in OIOI Web」</span>
								</a>
							</li>
							<li class="mb-[20px] overflow-hidden whitespace-nowrap text-ellipsis">
								<a href="https://pinocchiop.com/news/989" class = "hover:text-black hover:bg-white  w-full py-[4px] px-[15px] lg:py-[8px] lg:px-[23px] text-white text-[20px] bg-transparent block rounded-lg overflow-hidden text-ellipsis border-white border-solid border-2">
									<time class="pr-[20px] hidden lg:inline-block">2024.1.26</time>
									<span class="tracking-widest">新曲『Aじゃないか』MV公開</span>
								</a>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="mb-[20px]">
						<a href="">
							<img src="https://pinocchiop.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/META_banner-for-HP.png" class="w-full h-auto">
